casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Tod Kevin HOUTHOOFD, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157740
COA: 332323 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 16, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendant-appellant to file a pro per supplement to the application for leave to appeal is GRANTED. The supplement submitted on May 10, 2018, is accepted for filing.
